*1. Find linear interpolation at x = 1.5.
X = [0 1 2];
Y = [1 3 2];
x = 1.5;
y = interp1(X, Y, x);
plot(X(:), Y(:), x, y, 'o')
xlabel('x')
ylabel('y')
title(sprintf('Linear interpolation at x = %g', x))
grid on
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

*2. Plot cubic spline interpolation.
X = [0 1 2];
Y = [1 3 2];
x = linspace(0, 2, 100);
y = interp1(X, Y, x, 'PCHIP');
plot(x, y, X, Y, 'o')
xlabel('x')
ylabel('y')
title('Cubic Spline Interpolation')
grid on
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

























